com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.extensions

Interface ISCUIPostAuthenticationProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISCUISessionAware
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SCUIAdditionalThemeSupport

    public interface ISCUIPostAuthenticationProvider
extends ISCUISessionAware
    All application provided PostAuthenticationProvider will need to implement this class. It exposes the postAuthenticate() method. This provider is expected to handle the process after authentication of the user. ISCUIPostAuthenticationProvider is SessionAware which means that it is dependent on the Session validity. rasrinivasan
